				\begin{document}$\widehat {\mathbf {\Sigma }}$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M22"><mml:mover accent="false"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold">Σ</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mo>^</mml:mo></mml:mover></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2018_2185_Article_IEq8.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is the estimate of the covariance matrix <italic>C</italic><italic>o</italic><italic>v</italic>(<bold>U</bold>).</p>
      <p>Under <italic>H</italic>0′, the estimated covariance matrix <inline-formula id="IEq9"><alternatives><tex-math id="M23">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
